    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="container-xxl nlca-detail-main py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <!-- O Level Information -->
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <!-- Program Overview -->
                    <div class="nlca-detail-section mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h3 nlca-section-title mb-4">Program Overview</h2>
                        <div class="nlca-detail-body text-muted lh-lg">
                            <p>The Ordinary Level (O Level) program at Rusumo High School spans three years (Senior 1 to Senior 3) and provides students with a comprehensive, well-rounded education based on the Rwanda Education Board (REB) curriculum framework.</p>
                            
                            <p>Our O Level program is designed to:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Build strong academic foundations across all subject areas</li>
                                <li>Develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills</li>
                                <li>Foster character development and discipline</li>
                                <li>Prepare students for Advanced Level studies (A Level)</li>
                                <li>Cultivate practical skills and creativity</li>
                                <li>Promote active participation in school activities</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Core Subjects -->
                    <div class="nlca-detail-section mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h3 nlca-section-title mb-4">Curriculum Structure</h2>
                        <div class="nlca-detail-body text-muted lh-lg">
                            <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3">Core Subjects</h4>
                            <p>All students study the following core subjects:</p>
                            <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="card border-0 bg-light h-100">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h6 class="card-title text-primary"><i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i>Languages</h6>
                                            <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                <li>English Language</li>
                                                <li>French Language</li>
                                                <li>Kinyarwanda Language</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="card border-0 bg-light h-100">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h6 class="card-title text-primary"><i class="fas fa-calculator me-2"></i>Mathematics & Sciences</h6>
                                            <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                <li>Mathematics</li>
                                                <li>Physics</li>
                                                <li>Chemistry</li>
                                                <li>Biology</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3">Additional Core Subjects</h4>
                            <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="card border-0 bg-light h-100">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h6 class="card-title text-primary"><i class="fas fa-globe me-2"></i>Social Sciences</h6>
                                            <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                <li>History</li>
                                                <li>Geography</li>
                                                <li>Civics & Constitution</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="card border-0 bg-light h-100">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h6 class="card-title text-primary"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard me-2"></i>Other Subjects</h6>
                                            <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                <li>Physical Education</li>
                                                <li>Information Technology</li>
                                                <li>Life Skills Education</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3">Elective Subjects</h4>
                            <p>Students have the opportunity to choose elective subjects based on their interests and strengths, which may include:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Business Studies</li>
                                <li>Economics</li>
                                <li>Literature in English</li>
                                <li>Design and Technology</li>
                                <li>Visual Arts</li>
                                <li>Music (where available)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Learning Approach -->
                    <div class="nlca-detail-section mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h3 nlca-section-title mb-4">Teaching & Learning Approach</h2>
                        <div class="nlca-detail-body text-muted lh-lg">
                            <p>Our O Level program employs student-centered, active learning methodologies that include:</p>
                            <div class="alert alert-light border border-primary rounded-3 p-4" role="note">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-3 mt-1"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-1">Interactive Classes</h6>
                                        <p class="mb-0 small">Engaging lessons with student participation, discussions, and hands-on activities</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-3 mt-1"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-1">Practical Experiments</h6>
                                        <p class="mb-0 small">Laboratory work in science subjects to reinforce theoretical knowledge</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-3 mt-1"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-1">Research Projects</h6>
                                        <p class="mb-0 small">Independent and group projects to develop research and collaboration skills</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-3 mt-1"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-1">Technology Integration</h6>
                                        <p class="mb-0 small">Use of modern technology and ICT tools for enhanced learning</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-3 mt-1"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-1">Assessment & Feedback</h6>
                                        <p class="mb-0 small">Regular assessments with constructive feedback to guide improvement</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Progression to A Level -->
                    <div class="nlca-detail-section">
                        <h2 class="h3 nlca-section-title mb-4">Progression to Advanced Level</h2>
                        <div class="nlca-detail-body text-muted lh-lg">
                            <p>Upon successful completion of the O Level program (S3), students may progress to our Advanced Level (A Level) program if they meet the academic requirements and wish to continue their studies with us.</p>
                            
                            <p><strong>At A Level, students can choose from four specialized S4 streams:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>MS1</strong> - Maths and Sciences One</li>
                                <li><strong>MS2</strong> - Maths and Sciences Two</li>
                                <li><strong>ARH</strong> - Art and Humanities</li>
                                <li><strong>LGG</strong> - Languages</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <p><strong>Followed by further specialization in S5-S6 with seven combinations:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>PCM, MPG, MEG, PCB, HGL, LFK, MCB</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <p class="mt-3"><a href="../programs/secondary-section.html" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" wire:navigate.hover><i class="fas fa-arrow-right me-2"></i>Learn more about A Level</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

